room_title: Escape room "Yin Yang" by Escape Room Missouri City in Houston
review: We had a blast. My almost 15-year-old and 12-year-old really enjoyed it.

room_title: Escape room "Yin Yang" by Escape Room Missouri City in Houston
review: We had such a great time! The staff were fun and welcoming. The Yin Yang room was tough! If we had 5 more minutes we could have finished. Our biggest mistake was not taking advantage of the clues earlier in the game. We will be going again soon to try another room.

room_title: Escape room "Yin Yang" by Escape Room Missouri City in Houston
review: This was a great place for entertainment for our group of escape room enthusiasts. The puzzles in the Yin Yang room were the right level of challenging and logical. The room decor and props were well made and thought out. The hosts/owners/and game masters did a great job! We will definitely be returning soon for the next challenge of the three other rooms!
